指控涉及多份报道，称该主播的真名是 Guy Beahm，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2020/6/26/21304907/dr-disrespect-twitch-ban-no-reason-given&quot;>;因通过 Twitch Whispers 向未成年人发送不当消息而于 2020 年被 Twitch 禁止&lt;/a>;通讯应用程序。当比姆被封禁时，他和 Twitch 都没有解释原因，让这件事在四年内成为一个谜。然而，上周晚些时候，前 Twitch 成员科迪·康纳斯 (Cody Conners)...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188157/dr-disrespect-youtube -channel-demonetization-partner-program&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188157/dr-disrespect-youtube-channel-demonetization-partner-program" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188157/dr-disrespect-youtube-channel-demonetization-partner-program</id><author><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-28T11:23:49-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-28T11:23:49-04:00</updated><title> AT&amp;T Next Up Anytime 可让您每年获得 3 次手机升级，但价格并不便宜</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;AT&amp;amp;amp;T 徽标，带有红色和橙色背景插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/exGw8gZg-8GhSUsvy27KHj0OtBw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73433569/STK158_ATT_02.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7TKLuK&quot;>;AT&amp;T 宣布 &lt;a href=&quot;https://about.att.com/blogs/2024/next- up-anytime.html&quot;>;Next Up Anytime&lt;/a>;，这是一项针对 AT&amp;T 分期付款计划客户的新早期升级计划，将于 7 月 16 日开始提供。每月 10 美元，比 AT&amp;T 现有的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.att.com/ wireless/how-to-upgrade-your-cellphone/%E2%80%AF&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;每月 6 美元的 Next Up 附加组件&lt;/a>;，但订阅者可以选择只需完成一次分期付款即可升级智能手机，每年最多可升级三次。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;wu20il&quot;>;新计划推出后，新计划将不再向新用户提供更便宜的 Next Up客户，但已经拥有它的人将能够保留它，直到他们升级设备。借助 Next Up，客户在还清一半费用后，就可以通过每月分期付款或一次性一次性付款的方式立即以旧换新并升级他们的设备...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188060/att-smartphones-next-up-anytime-upgrade&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188060/att-smartphones-next-up-anytime-upgrade" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188060/att-smartphones-next-up-anytime-upgrade</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-28T11:10:33-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-28T11:10:33-04:00</updated><title> The Verge 夏季“进”/“出”名单</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片拼贴画，两个箭头进出敞开的门口。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TIzkzcelPMBdG6zu6yK3TNG9wsg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73433518/247170_Ins_and_Outs_CVirginiaA.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;在我们制作这个网站的同时享受乐趣。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/24188055/the-verge-summer-in-out-list-trends&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24188055/the-verge-summer-in-out-list-trends" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24188055/the-verge-summer-in-out-list-trends</id><author><name>佐藤米娅</name></author></entry></feed>